Study any religion. They all have beliefs that you will either relate with 
or not:  People walking counter-clock wise around a black cube at Mecca;  
people praying to a goat and drinking blood; Voodoo, curses and witchcraft; 
praying to a cow etc..  Or the religion of modern Science and evolution 
(which is a religion today).  I look forward to your future takes on those 
religions.﻿
